'''Sund''' was the company that manufactured the [[x2-100 laser cannon]], a popular weapon to mount on [[Snowspeeder/Legends|snowspeeders]]. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] utilized their product during the [[Battle of Hoth/Legends|Battle of Hoth]].

